    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/4234e41b34b3f1b4f8c77c2207a3b53b.avif?t=1763063723\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras_big/4234e41b34b3f1b4f8c77c2207a3b53b.avif?t=1763063723 width=800 height=47 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>一款只需一个按钮就能畅玩的节奏游戏合集！</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受多样的视觉风格和地道的巴西节奏——精准敲击每一拍，成为真正的节奏大师！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/64a901e9997e3e7c4f183a6b5b5008b7.poster.avif?t=1763063723\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/64a901e9997e3e7c4f183a6b5b5008b7.webm?t=1763063723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/64a901e9997e3e7c4f183a6b5b5008b7.mp4?t=1763063723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>节奏曼狂</strong>采用灵感来源于经典主机节奏游戏的单按钮机制，提供快速上手、轻松畅玩的体验，适合新手玩家和资深节奏游戏爱好者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏收录了从波萨诺瓦到桑巴、阿谢、帕戈吉、巴西放克等多种原创音乐风格，并由获奖的巴西插画师们打造出绚丽的视觉效果，让每一场迷你游戏都充满节奏与色彩的爆发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/a6265cf035745bb52d116d5c24097d28.poster.avif?t=1763063723\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/a6265cf035745bb52d116d5c24097d28.webm?t=1763063723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/a6265cf035745bb52d116d5c24097d28.mp4?t=1763063723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/c30d3ec6229998be7eb1d51531ebd4ab.avif?t=1763063723\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras_big/c30d3ec6229998be7eb1d51531ebd4ab.avif?t=1763063723 width=800 height=47 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>快速开始游戏: </strong>打开游戏，几秒内即可开始畅玩，适合短暂休闲或长时间畅玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>数十款迷你游戏: </strong>掌握不同主题下的节奏挑战——放风筝、用表情包回复群聊、搬运行李、拯救卡在体育馆屋顶的球等等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>超级混合模式:</strong> 挑战自己，体验将多个关卡融合在一起的高强度节奏挑战<strong>。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全面支持手柄:</strong> 支持键盘、鼠标或你最喜欢的游戏手柄自由畅玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam成就系统: </strong>通过通关、刷新个人纪录和完成额外挑战来解锁成就。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>跳入节奏的世界——跳入节奏曼狂！</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/415387e95afab2c0bd81dcc180abf649.avif?t=1763063723\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras_big/415387e95afab2c0bd81dcc180abf649.avif?t=1763063723 width=800 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/89e4c56ce9fb577933e79fd1921c73ba.poster.avif?t=1763063723\" width=616 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/89e4c56ce9fb577933e79fd1921c73ba.webm?t=1763063723\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322070/extras/89e4c56ce9fb577933e79fd1921c73ba.mp4?t=1763063723\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
